'''2013年12月貝魯特爆炸案'''是發生於2013年12月27日，在[[黎巴嫩|黎巴嫩]][[貝魯特|貝魯特]][[貝魯特中央區|貝魯特中央區]]的[[汽車炸彈|汽車炸彈]]攻擊事件，總共造成七人喪生，71人受傷<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-25524729|title=Beirut blast kills Sunni ex-minister Mohamad Chatah|date=2013-12-27|website=bbc.co.uk|publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|accessdate=2013-12-27|archive-date=2013-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131227171712/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-25524729|dead-url=no}}</ref>。罹難者當中，還包括前黎巴嫩部長、駐美國大使{{link-en|穆罕默德·沙塔赫|Mohamad Chatah}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/mohamad-chatah-lebanese-ex-minister-killed-in-beirut-bombing-1.2476861|title=Mohamad Chatah, Lebanese ex-minister, killed in Beirut bombing|date=2013-12-27|website=cbc.ca|publisher=[[CBC|CBC]]|accessdate=2013-12-27|archive-date=2017-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171012115938/http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/mohamad-chatah-lebanese-ex-minister-killed-in-beirut-bombing-1.2476861|dead-url=no}}</ref>。目前仍無何方承認發動攻擊<ref>{{cite web|url=http://cnn.com/2013/12/27/world/meast/lebanon-explosion/|title=Lebanon's Chatah -- friend of U.S., enemy of Assad, Hezbollah -- killed|last1=Abedine|first1=Saad|last2=Yan|first2=Holly|last3=Basil|first3=Yousuf|date=27 December 2013|website=cnn.com|publisher=[[CNN|CNN]]|accessdate=27 December 2013|archive-date=2019-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608111146/https://www.cnn.com/2013/12/27/world/meast/lebanon-explosion/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，然而[[真主黨|真主黨]]被指控曾向眾多黎巴嫩官員進行襲擊行為<ref name=reuters>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/12/27/us-syria-crisis-beirut-bomb-idUSBRE9BQ01H20131227|title=Beirut bomb kills Lebanese ex-minister who opposed Assad|last1=Nakhoul|first1=Samia|last2=Kalin|first2=Stephen|date=2013-12-27|website=reuters.com|publisher=[[路透社|路透社]]|accessdate=2013-12-28|archive-date=2014-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140213053854/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/12/27/us-syria-crisis-beirut-bomb-idUSBRE9BQ01H20131227|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

七名喪生者當中，有六名死於現場，一位則在醫院因傷重不治<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.news.com.au/world/teen-in-beirut-bombing-selfie-dies/story-fndir2ev-1226791315034|title=Teen in Beirut bombing 'selfie' dies|date=2013-12-29|website=news.com.au|publisher=News Limited|accessdate=2013-12-29|archive-date=2016-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160103064547/http://www.news.com.au/world/teen-in-beirut-bombing-selfie-dies/story-fndir2ev-1226791315034|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

